title: 177: Draft Don'ts with Lance Zierlein
itunes:title: 177: Draft Don'ts with Lance Zierlein
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are joined by Lance Zierlein to debate if the Jets should take a first-round QB, should the Browns draft anyone not named Myles Garrett 1st overall, and is the Patrick Mahomes buzz warranted?
